// Node Js introduction

--> Nodejs is an open source run-time server environment.
--> Nodejs allows you to run javascript on server.


// introduction

--> Nodejs is an open source server environment.
--> Nodejs is Free.
--> Nodejs runs on various platforms.
--> Nodejs uses javascript on server.

*/* Nodejs runs single threaded, non-blocking, asynchronous programming, which is very memory efficient. */*


// Get Started 

--> Download Nodejs from its official website.

--> Initiate the Nodejs file,
        write / node file.js ---> on command line.

